}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[217,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Lottie.purs","start":[214,1]},"title":"showLottiePlayback"}],"comments":"Lottie playback configuration.\n\nControls how the animation plays:\n- Autoplay on load or wait for trigger\n- Loop count (finite or infinite)\n- Playback speed (1.0 = normal, 0.5 = half speed, 2.0 = double)\n- Direction (forward, reverse, alternate ping-pong)\n- Initial delay before starting\n\n## Speed Bounds\n\nSpeed is clamped to 0.1 to 10.0:\n- Below 0.1 is effectively paused\n- Above 10.0 is too fast to perceive\n\n## Loop Behavior\n\n- `LoopInfinite`: Loop forever until stopped\n- `LoopCount n`: Play n times then stop\n- `LoopCount 1`: Play once (same as playOnce)\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[199,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Lottie.purs","start":[191,1]},"title":"LottiePlayback"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create playback config with full options\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["autoplay",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["loop",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Lottie"],"LoopMode"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["speed",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["direction",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Lottie"],"PlaybackDirection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["delayMs",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["pauseOnHoverEx